'''施拉達·卡普爾'''（[[印度語|印度語]]：श्रद्धा कपूर，[[英語|英語]]：{{lang-en|Shraddha Kapoor}}，{{bd|1992年|3月3日|catIdx=Kapoor, Shraddha}}<ref>[http://m.koimoi.com/actress/shraddha-kapoor "Shraddha Kapoor"] {{Wayback|url=http://m.koimoi.com/actress/shraddha-kapoor |date=20160105011714 }}, Koimoi.</ref>）是[[印度|印度]][[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]女演員。卡普爾的父親Shakti Kapoor是一名擁有[[旁遮普人|旁遮普血統]]演員，母親則是[[馬拉地人|馬拉地人]]<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/i-m-playing-a-complete-marathi-mulgi-shraddha-kapoor/article1-913424.aspx "I’m playing a complete marathi mulgi: Shraddha Kapoor"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/i-m-playing-a-complete-marathi-mulgi-shraddha-kapoor/article1-913424.aspx |date=20141102001544 }}, Hindustan Times, 14 August 2012.</ref>。

她在2010年和巨星[[阿米塔布·巴沙坎|阿米塔布·巴沙坎]]等人合作演出了她首套電影《Teen Patti》，即使該電影票房慘淡，卡普爾的演出使她獲得了2011年[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]的最佳女新人提名<ref>[http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/dream-come-true-to-work-with-big-b-say-teen-patti-debutant-actors_52660.html "Dream come true to work with Big B, say 'Teen Patti' debutant actors"] {{Wayback|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/bollywood/dream-come-true-to-work-with-big-b-say-teen-patti-debutant-actors_52660.html |date=20160304212926 }}, ZeeNews India, 30 January 2010.</ref>。2011年，她与[[雅什－拉吉影片公司|雅什－拉吉影片公司]]签电影合约，並首次主演电影《亲爱的，你完了》（Luv Ka The End）<ref>[http://archive.mid-day.com/entertainment/2012/jun/160612-Shraddha-Kapoor-shown-the-door-by-Yash-and-Aditya-Chopra.htm "Shraddha Kapoor shown the door by Yash and Aditya Chopra"] {{Wayback|url=http://archive.mid-day.com/entertainment/2012/jun/160612-Shraddha-Kapoor-shown-the-door-by-Yash-and-Aditya-Chopra.htm |date=20180915080906 }}, Mid Day, 16 June 2012.</ref>。2013年，卡普爾拍攝了大熱電影《誓愛如歌2》（Aashiqui 2），她的演出備受影評人讚賞<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Reviews/Anupama-Chopra-s-review-Aashiqui-2/Article1-1050953.aspx "Anupama Chopra's review: Aashiqui 2"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Reviews/Anupama-Chopra-s-review-Aashiqui-2/Article1-1050953.aspx |date=20141214193300 }}, Hindustan Times, 26 April 2013.</ref>。《誓愛如歌2》也為她帶來[[第59屆印度電影觀眾獎|第59屆印度電影觀眾獎]]的最佳女主角提名<ref>[http://www.filmfare.com/news/59th-idea-filmfare-awards-nominations-5138.html "59th Idea Filmfare Awards Nominations"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmfare.com/news/59th-idea-filmfare-awards-nominations-5138.html |date=20140115044052 }}, Filmfare, 13 January 2014.</ref>。

